title: Desert Eagle
lyrics:

Sugar high, you gon' want some more
Of that do-si-do (Dosi')
Of that dosi', do-si-do
That do-si-do (Dosi')
Of that do-si-do (Do-si-do, do-si-do, do-si-do)
